[phone chimes]

788
00:40:09.323 --> 00:40:11.325
[exhales sharply]

789
00:40:18.541 --> 00:40:20.543
[laughs]

790
00:40:27.049 --> 00:40:30.136
Oh shit. Oh my God.

791
00:40:37.685 --> 00:40:39.270
[laughing continues]

792
00:40:57.288 --> 00:40:58.330
[chuckles]

793
00:41:16.932 --> 00:41:18.934
[pensive music continues]

794
00:41:41.874 --> 00:41:43.083
