on my own merit?

820
00:43:39.992 --> 00:43:41.869
I finally feel useful now.

821
00:43:42.369 --> 00:43:43.787
This is what you wanted.

822
00:43:43.871 --> 00:43:46.415
Okay. I'll accept it
if you can look me in the eye

823
