and tell me you're not into Eunice.

824
00:43:48.250 --> 00:43:49.960
[scoffs]

825
00:43:55.549 --> 00:43:57.760
I mean. I'm not into her.

826
00:43:57.843 --> 00:43:58.886
[scoffs]

827
