852
00:45:55.294 --> 00:45:57.421
-[Ashley grunts]
-Ashley! What the fuck?

853
00:45:57.504 --> 00:45:59.840
[grunts. pants]

854
00:46:00.674 --> 00:46:02.259
[tires squeal]

855
00:46:02.342 --> 00:46:05.512
He's gonna leave me.
He's gonna fucking leave me.

856
00:46:05.596 --> 00:46:06.513
Stop!

857
00:46:06.597 --> 00:46:09.141
I'm fine. I'm just processing.

858
00:46:09.224 --> 00:46:10.768
-Ash!
-[breathing heavily]

859
00:46:10.851 --> 00:46:13.896
-Ashley. what are you doing?
-Just give me some space. please!

860
00:46:15.397 --> 00:46:19.777
<i>Just grab yourself. bring your body</i>
<i>'Cause uptown funk gonna give it to ya!</i>

861
00:46:20.652 --> 00:46:22.613
[Ashley grunting]

862
00:46:22.696 --> 00:46:24.281
Fuck! Shit!

863
00:46:24.364 --> 00:46:26.158
[grunts. screams]

864
